Q1.What is the role of AWS/Azure/GCP in DevOps?
DevOps aims for continuous innovation and faster delivery of software from development through operations, Cloud Operations also call for continuous operations & improvement — but in cloud environments.
DevOps and Cloud are likely to become all-rounder and organizations will need greater discipline to craft and adhere to a strategy that leads to stability and consistency. It is intriguing for project teams to choose the latest technology or to select a cloud vendor that offers the simplest interface. But in enterprises, there are various factors to consider during business services operationalizing, and diversity breeds complexity. To learn about those factors, you can take DevOps training and can tide over software developers and operations.
